<br>
Many times a board gets side tracked on to legitemit concerns.  Many other times the posts turn into flame wars.  It's hard to keep the peace and it's hard to moderate the boards.   <br>
<br>
Everyone gets mad nowand again and everyone flames now and again.  I guess if you must clean up the boards then the best thing would be to just delete any and all flameing posts.  Each time you do this state that it was deleted do to flame content.  Then politely ask the flamer to repost with out flames.  <br>
